  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Electrical Impedance Myography Measurements</measure>
    <time_frame>Baseline (all subjects) &amp; 3 months, 6 months, 1 year for returning subjects only</time_frame>
    <description>Up to 11 muscles will be measured using EIM technology. These muscles include: Right Lateral Deltoid, Right Biceps, Right Triceps, Right Wrist Flexors, Right Wrist Extensors, Right Vastus Lateralis, Right Tibialis Anterior, Right Gastrocnemius, Right Gluteus Medius, Right Biceps Femoris, and Right Thoracic Parapinal.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
